<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>{% block title %}Welcome!{% endblock %}</title>
    {% block stylesheets %}{{ encore_entry_link_tags('app') }}{% endblock %}
    <style>
        body {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            background-image: linear-gradient(to top, #F0F0F0, #F9F9F9);
            background-repeat: no-repeat;
        }
        header{
            /* 0 flex-grow, 0 flex-shrink, auto flex-basis */
            flex: 0 0 auto;
        }
        .main-content{
            /* 1 flex-grow, 0 flex-shrink, auto flex-basis */
            flex: 1 0 auto;
        }
        footer{
            /* 0 flex-grow, 0 flex-shrink, auto flex-basis */
            flex: 0 0 auto;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<header>
    <div class="row m-0 justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-8 m-0 p-0 shadow background-white">
            <div class="row justify-content-between border-bottom p-4 m-0">
                <div class="col-6">
                    <h1><a href="/" class="text-dark">Блог одного программиста</a></h1>
                </div>
                <div class="col-6">
                    <b>Заметки о программировании преимущественно на PHP,<br> заметки о системном администрировании</b>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</header>
    <section class="main-content">
        <div class="row  m-0 justify-content-center h-100">
            <div class="col-8 shadow" style="background: white;">
                {% for message in app.session.flashBag.get('notice') %}
                    <div class="col-12 alert alert-success p-0 m-0" role="alert">
                        {{ message|trans }}
                        <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="alert" aria-label="Close">
                            <span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
                        </button>
                    </div>
                {% endfor %}
                {% for message in app.session.flashBag.get('error') %}
                    <div class=" col-12 alert alert-danger p-3 mt-2" role="alert">
                        {{ message }}
                        <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="alert" aria-label="Close">
                            <span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
                        </button>
                    </div>
                {% endfor %}
                <div class="col-12 pt-3">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-9 pt-2 pl-4 pr-4 mt-0 ml-0 mr-0 mb-3">
                            {% block body %}{% endblock %}
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-3 border-left pt-2 mt-0 ml-0 mr-0 mb-3">
                            navigation
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <footer>
        <div class="row m-0 justify-content-center ">
            <div class="col-8 m-0 p-0 shadow background-white p-4 text-center border-top">
                Все материалы принадлежат автору. Публикация возможна с согласия автора. 2019. <a href="mailto:s@istranet.ru">Анатолий Шадрин</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>
    {% block javascripts %}{{ encore_entry_script_tags('app') }}{% endblock %}
    </body>
</html>
